  work (i.e. before 10th each 4th month).  Reported by Giovanni Addabbo.
o Doesn't calculate years right (< 8. May)
o MoreReq sometimes cause enforcer hits.  Normally the first time it is shown
o Input rawchars isn't fast enough.  All characters aren't rendered
o Purge module does not work at all!

