*** BETA RELEASES *********************************************************************
Beta Release 3.1.1: (04.07.95)
INT: Better initializing of EasyGadgets attributes
FIX: V2.x import module did not convert the day-field for events of EXACT DATE
     type.  Reported by Nick Ridley.
FIX: V2.x import module always set the day of AFTER DATE events to 1.
FIX: V2.x import module now uses a slightly more secure method to parse textstrings.
FIX: Slightly optimized V2.x project parsing.
FIX: Speeded up clicking on dirs significantly.
FIX: Optimized update of text, attrib and date windows.
FIX: HELP Search/Replace menu item did not show.
FIX: Some links in the document were not legal.
FIX: Help on menus did not work when using other languages.
FIX: Optimized menu help.
FIX: Installer should not set the language=<> tooltype.
FIX: Pressing HELP when the mousepointer was over a MENUTITLE caused an enforcer hit.
FIX: Small changes to the norsk and nynorsk catalogs.
FIX: Count years did not take the day and month into account.
FIX: Small changes to the Workbench font.
FIX: Better handling of memory by the dynamic menu-structure.  Faster resetting.
     Uses less memory.
FIX: Recall.key needs to be placed in the Recall drawer and not in S:
FIX: Cleaned up the catalog description.

NEW: Copy-button in Event/Text/Date windows
NEW: Recall will now use system pens under WB3.0 and higher when using own screen.
NEW: New HELP menu displayed in the rightmost corner of the screen.
NEW: About menu item moved to help-menu.
NEW: Added hotkey for menu item 'Iconify'.
NEW: When necessary the entire Attributes window is ghosted instead of all its
     gadgets.  This speeds up the update considerably.
NEW: Recall Preferences now automatically activates the first event in the project.

